                "PLATE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Energies and angular distributions  of",
                "3He particles were measured with a broad range magnetic",
                "spectrograph and registered on nuclear emulsions Z.T.F.",
                " (Russian) type K of the 100 micro-m thickness. During",
                "exposures the emulsions were placed in vacuum."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In addition a scintillation counter was used as",
                "a monitor, viewing a thin gold target at a fixed angle",
                "of about 30 degr. with respect to the incident beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Al target with the thickness of 0.4 mg/cm2 was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
